9. **llms.txt** — Complete with all services, location pages, blog posts, contact info, social links, and UAE emirates coverage.

10. **Internal Linking** — Blog posts link to related services via `internal-links.ts`. Homepage links to all service pages. Services hub links to all individual service pages.

11. **Keyword Targeting** — All target keywords appear naturally on the right pages.

12. **Local SEO** — NAP consistent across schema and contact page. "Serving all UAE emirates" messaging present.

13. **Images** — Using Next.js `<Image>` component with descriptive alt text.

